<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0559b03" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0559b03">曰文殊師利秦言妙德經云曾<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>成佛名曰龍種尊也</note>
<note n="0560b01" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0560b01">言不見有異相也魔樂著五欲不求出世故繫以生死異學雖求出世而執著<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>己</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>道故繫以邪見大士觀生死同涅槃故能不捨觀邪見同正見故能不動</note>
<note n="0560b02" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0560b02">四大本性自無患也眾<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>緣</corr><sic>綠</sic></choice>既會增損相尅患乃生耳欲言有病本性自無欲言無病相假而有故病非地亦不離地餘大類此</note>
<note n="0560b07" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0560b07">無漏無為其法無相非妄想所能攀緣所得攀緣者三界而<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>耳</note>
<note n="0561b01" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0561b01">曰觀空不取涉有不著是名巧方便也今明六住<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>還未能無礙當其觀空無所取著及其出觀淨國化人則生見取相拙于涉動妙于淨觀故言無方便而有慧</note>
<note n="0561b11" resp="#resp3" type="mod_biao" target="#nkr_note_mod_biao_0561b11">雖自修<choice cb:resp="#resp2"><corr>己</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>根而善知人根彼我俱順也</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0559b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b03">曰文殊師利秦言妙德經云曾巳成佛名曰龍種尊也</note>
<note n="0559b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b04">近知菩薩儀式遠入諸佛秘藏秘藏謂身口意秘密之藏</note>
<note n="0559b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b05">餘聲聞專以離苦為心不求深法故不同舉耳五百智慧深入樂問深法所以俱行</note>
<note n="0559b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b06">空室去侍以生言端事證于後</note>
<note n="0559b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b07">曰發斯念者因以空室示以虗納之懷有去故空密在用標宗致也現神力者念之使也</note>
<note n="0559b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b08">大士法身進止不違實相實相不來以之而來實相無見以之相見不來而能來不見而能見法身若此善如之</note>
<note n="0559b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b09">法身無生況復有形既無有形病何由起然為彼受生不得無形不得無病故因其久近與之同病</note>
<note n="0559b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b10">文殊以事問居士以理答</note>
<note n="0559b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0559b11">是非之域妄想所存若能空虗其懷冥心真境有無一觀者雖智周萬物未始為有幽塗無照未始為無</note>
<note n="0560b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b01">言不見有異相也魔樂著五欲不求出世故繫以生死異學雖求出世而執著巳道故繫以邪見大士觀生死同涅槃故能不捨觀邪見同正見故能不動</note>
<note n="0560b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b02">四大本性自無患也眾綠既會增損相尅患乃生耳欲言有病本性自無欲言無病相假而有故病非地亦不離地餘大類此</note>
<note n="0560b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b03">外國法從生至終所作福業一一書記若命終時傍人為說令恃福無畏</note>
<note n="0560b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b04">向以法遣我自此以下以空遣法也</note>
<note n="0560b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b05">我為萬物主萬物為我所若離我我所則無法不離</note>
<note n="0560b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b06">受謂苦樂捨三受若能解受無受則能為物受生而忍受三受也</note>
<note n="0560b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b07">無漏無為其法無相非妄想所能攀緣所得攀緣者三界而巳耳</note>
<note n="0560b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b08">二見內有妄想外有諸法二虗假終無得</note>
<note n="0560b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b09">未能深入實相見有眾生心生愛著因此生悲名為愛見大悲</note>
<note n="0560b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0560b10">若能除愛即棄捨結業受法化生自在無礙也</note>
<note n="0561b01" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b01">曰觀空不取涉有不著是名巧方便也今明六住巳還未能無礙當其觀空無所取著及其出觀淨國化人則生見取相拙于涉動妙于淨觀故言無方便而有慧</note>
<note n="0561b02" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b02">生死可厭而不厭善處嶮難故名方便</note>
<note n="0561b03" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b03">離身則無病故不相離新故之名出于先後眾緣所成誰先誰後則泯新故而入實相故名慧而與彼同疾不取涅槃謂之方便自調初說即其事也慰喻自調略為權智權智此經之關要</note>
<note n="0561b04" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b04">功行未足而求至足之果名非時求</note>
<note n="0561b05" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b05">觀無生是取證法不入正位明不證也</note>
<note n="0561b06" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b06">觀緣起斷邪見之道也而反同邪見豈二乘之所能乎</note>
<note n="0561b07" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b07">三界即法性處之何所壞也</note>
<note n="0561b08" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b08">行無作欲不造生死而方現受身也</note>
<note n="0561b09" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b09">菩薩觀漏即是無漏故能永處生死與之同漏豈漏盡而自異于漏乎</note>
<note n="0561b10" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b10">如意足神通之因也</note>
<note n="0561b11" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b11">雖自修巳根而善知人根彼我俱順也</note>
<note n="0561b12" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b12">雖同聲聞根力覺道其志常在佛行</note>
<note n="0561b13" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b13">究竟淨相理無形像而隨彼所應現若干象</note>
<note n="0561b14" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0561b14">雖現成佛轉法輪入涅槃而不永滅還入生死脩菩薩法如上所列豈二乘之所能乎獨菩薩行耳</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
